@baseUrl = https://localhost:7080
@eventId = {{createEvent.response.body.id}}
@personId = {{getEvent.response.body.people[0].id}}

### Get all events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/event

### Create a new event
# @name createEvent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tech Conference 2025",
  "date": "2025-06-15T09:00:00Z",
  "description": "Annual technology conference"
}

### Get event by ID
# @name getEvent
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/event/{{eventId}}

### Upload CSV with attendees
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/event/{{eventId}}/upload-csv
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="attendees.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

Name,Email
John Doe,john.doe@example.com
Jane Smith,jane.smith@example.com
Bob Johnson,bob.johnson@example.com
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Check in a person
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/checkin/{{eventId}}/person/{{personId}}

### Get check-in status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/checkin/status/{{eventId}}

### Get checked-in people
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/event/{{eventId}}/checked-in

### Get not checked-in people
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/event/{{eventId}}/not-checked-in

### Delete an event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/event/{{eventId}}
